        "Details": "Developed by Clan Wolverine before their annihilation by the other clans, the design's modular hardpoints were the inspiration for omnimech technology. After the annihilation of Clan Wolverine, most remaining Mercury II's were eventually decomissioned after study by the other clans. Armed with a wide variety of lasers, and equipped with a lot of jumpjets for mobility, the mech is able to move and strike reliably from vantage points before many opponents can react.<br><br>X-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
